  "description": "Validated and accurate prognostic testing is critical for precision\n medicine in uveal melanoma (UM). Our aims were to (1) prospectively\n validate an integrated prognostic classifier combining a 15-gene\n expression profile (15-GEP) and PRAME RNA expression, and (2) identify\n clinical variables that enhance the prognostic accuracy of the\n 15-GEP/PRAME classifier.",
  "license": "https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/legalcode",
  "version": "2",
